    "This section is targeted to the introduction of different aspects related to customer behaviour.",
    "In Sect. 3.1, we start by describing the most popular choice models and frequently used estimation techniques.",
    "Subsequently, model extensions related to the allowed number of item purchases or the incorporation of consideration sets are discussed in Sects.",
    "3.2 and 3.3, respectively.",
    "We terminate the section by a description of the impact of different sales channels on customer behaviour in Sect. 3.4."
